The final scheme we consider is neither in-plane Lagrangian nor in-plane Eulerian. Instead, the mesh is modeled as a separate 2D material with its own constitutive relations and associated dynamical equations. The mesh analogs of the stress vectors are then expressed as [cf. Eq. (14)]

