(67)

Equation (67) is solved with the Newton–Raphson method, where a sequence of progressively better

estimates of the membrane state [u] is generated. Given the jth estimate [u]j, the (j + 1)th estimate

is calculated according to

[u]j+1 = [u]j − [K]−j 1 r([u]j) ,

